            <section ID="id_link_bf3f60a7-8ee7-79d2-e053-2995a90aa498">
               <id root="bf44867e-98c5-9ea6-e053-2a95a90a120c"/>
               <code code="34071-1" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="WARNINGS SECTION"/>
               <title>WARNING</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>For external use on the skin only.
  <br/>
Severe injury may result from use internally or as a douche. Avoid contact with mucous membranes."
 </paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20210401"/>
            </section>
         </component>
         <component>
            <section ID="id_link_bf3f7ae2-f29b-693f-e053-2a95a90a0c93">
               <id root="bf44867e-98bd-9ea6-e053-2a95a90a120c"/>
               <code code="34067-9" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="INDICATIONS &amp; USAGE SECTION"/>
               <title>INDICATIONS AND USAGE</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Astringent, Alkaline, for superficial and deep festering wounds. for 1st, 2nd and 3rd ulcers and burns. grade. Ideal for people with diabetes.Úpply directly without diluting, on the affected area or use an impregnated gauze.</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20210401"/>
            </section>
         </component>
         <component>
            <section ID="id_link_bf3f720d-b7e2-edd1-e053-2a95a90a52e6">
               <id root="bf44867e-98be-9ea6-e053-2a95a90a120c"/>
               <code code="34068-7" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="DOSAGE &amp; ADMINISTRATION SECTION"/>
               <title>DOSAGE AND ADMINISTRATION</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>It Is Recommended to apply 3 to 5 times a day.</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20210401"/>
            </section>
         </component>
         <component>
            <section ID="id_link_bf3f7eb8-652b-53ee-e053-2995a90a1813">
